Available Tools: create_folder | move_file | copy_file | rename_file | delete_file | list_folder
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "path": "string", "destination": "string", "new_name": "string" }
Response Schema: { "path": "string", "entries": [{ "name": "string", "type": "file|folder", "size_bytes": number }], "status": "string" }

Question: Show all items in the downloads directory to identify large files for archival.
Call: { "func_call": "list_folder", "path": "/downloads", "destination": "", "new_name": "" }
Response: { "path": "/downloads", "entries": [{ "name": "setup_installer.exe", "type": "file", "size_bytes": 150000 }, { "name": "report_q2.pdf", "type": "file", "size_bytes": 32000 }, { "name": "images", "type": "folder", "size_bytes": 0 }, { "name": "temp_log.txt", "type": "file", "size_bytes": 850 }], "status": "success" }

Question: Rename the temporary log file to archive_log_2024.txt for long-term storage.
Call: { "func_call": "rename_file", "path": "/downloads/temp_log.txt", "destination": "", "new_name": "archive_log_2024.txt" }
Response: { "path": "/downloads", "entries": [{ "name": "setup_installer.exe", "type": "file", "size_bytes": 150000 }, { "name": "report_q2.pdf", "type": "file", "size_bytes": 32000 }, { "name": "images", "type": "folder", "size_bytes": 0 }, { "name": "archive_log_2024.txt", "type": "file", "size_bytes": 850 }], "status": "renamed" }

Question: Remove the old setup installer executable as the software is already installed.
Call: { "func_call": "delete_file", "path": "/downloads/setup_installer.exe", "destination": "", "new_name": "" }
Response: { "path": "/downloads", "entries": [{ "name": "report_q2.pdf", "type": "file", "size_bytes": 32000 }, { "name": "images", "type": "folder", "size_bytes": 0 }, { "name": "archive_log_2024.txt", "type": "file", "size_bytes": 850 }], "status": "deleted" }

